{"tid":675592,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦自己成日熄機，啱啱入load入桌面都照熄","createTime":"2018-05-23T15:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T18:54:39.000Z","uid":104390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d077259d0e8a77c3749e528c2c0f900d5afa06a7","tid":675592,"uid":104390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T15:36:22.000Z","msg":"我想問有無巴打知咩事？事源係上年十二月入開始，我部電腦一開game打就會熄機，我一開始已為係over load左個電壓急降先會熄，之後我就用啲燒機progamme 燒左部成個幾鐘，熄都無熄，睇返個log 溫度都係得～40度，跟住我就無理到佢因為最多唔打機，之後就開始愈黎愈差，有時會睇睇下youtube，到啱啱入load入desktop 都熄 ，但好搞笑嘅係，我熄曬啲電制，放佢一陣再開返機又會無事入得返desktop ，我都唔知係火牛出事，定底板定係windows出事，火牛用左3年，老母板用左～8年，有無巴打知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b1f60f1f26308d68c54391ccf98d156c750bb7","tid":675592,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c19af3abb30515e6ec61fa4f48c5faf8f92edf6e","tid":675592,"uid":104390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>maybe 電腦 你撳開機粒電源掣 痴咗裡面啲線 以為你長撳電源掣 強制關機<br />\n<br />\n利申試過</blockquote><br />\n應該唔會，因為佢好似一高loading就會熄"},{"pid":"ab12085c4c0faaae4f52ac946b84aad58a09cf2c","tid":675592,"uid":27356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:39:20.000Z","msg":"換左佢啦"},{"pid":"4d5b2dd969b8db8b1d4f72df255ad8f7c8f668b9","tid":675592,"uid":128210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c19af3abb30515e6ec61fa4f48c5faf8f92edf6e","tid":675592,"uid":104390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor